data.title: CONTRACTORS
data.text:
50

Confirm contact

Check the box if you succeed to contact the specified email address or phone number. It will only take a couple of seconds, but it will help you organize your contacts and allow other users to bypass broken contacts.

150

Add contact

If you found the correct email address or company phone number that is not listed on CONTRACTORS, add it and select the appropriate topic of questions for this address / number.

350

Another user confirmed the added contact

As a thank you, your limit will be further increased after another user uses the contact you added and confirms it.
